      <h3>
        Slither.io
      </h3>
      <h4>
        In slither.io, you become a snake eating nearby dots to become longer, avoiding running into other snakes. Snakes that run into other snakes die and drop their carcass that acts as food that other snakes can eat to become longer.
      </h4>
    </div>
    <div class="play-now">
